Text:
Thank you very much for the upload.

Do you think it would be possible to scan the small text at the bottom of certain pages with different contrast settings?  

It is very difficult to read, although from what I just looked into, it is apparently also very hard to read in the actual print edition.

http://www.thestar.com/living/food/article/1284356---secret-codes-and-comic-relief

"It wasn’t until the third issue of Adventure Time that I noticed the faint-green, 10-point type at the bottom of the pages, adding commentary or background information."
